Description: The HandiCamHD's go-anywhere design brings versatility to your shoots, while True HD resolution brings vivid clarity to your videos.   With the HandiCamHD, you can let your imagination run wild. In addition to a variety of battle-tested mounting options, the custom-built waterproof case keeps the HandiCamHD protected in any environment; sailing through the air or down to 60 feet below the water's surface, its safe, secure, and accessible. Unlike some portable action cameras, you can even check your footage right there on location, with a built-in LCD screen for playback.    Built-In LCD Screen:  Don't lug around a monitor or wait until you get home to watch your video - play it back right away, right on the spot, on a built-in LCD screen. Motion Detector:  The HandiCamHD's built-in motion detector is handy way to film your own stunts when your backup crew bows out. MicroSD and USB:  For ease and universal compatibility, footage is recorded onto removable Ultra Class MicroSD memory cards (up to 32 GB), and the HandiCamHD connects to your computer through USB. Description: Strap on the BulletCam 2.0 during your next adventure, and return with crips, action-packed HD footage of every epic moment. Plus, the BulletCam 2.0 is waterproof, shockproof, and comes with enough battery power to last all day.  Go ahead - take the plunge. Just make sure to strap on a BulletCam 2.0 so that we can come along for the ride. Whether windsurfing, snowboarding or base-jumping is your bag, you can bring home amazing, engaging footage with the BulletCam 2.0 on board. This sleek, high-quality action camera shoots Full HD video from a shockproof, waterproof, lightweight aluminum design. A glass fisheye lens brings in a wide field of view, while video stabilization technology makes your footage smoother than a steep slope loaded with fresh powder. Two long-lasting batteries provide you eight straight hours of power, and the BulletCam 2.0's various mounting options keep it safe and secure for every minute of action.    Attractive Aerodynamic Design: The BulletCam 2.0's black anodized aluminum body has style in mind. It'll blend in without adding bulk, and won't give you any extra resistance while you whip down the slopes.  Waterproof and Shockproof: The BulletCam 2.0 is built for any condition. Long falls, wet weather, and bumpy roads will all fail to intimidate it. It's resistant to shock, moisture, pain, and fear.   That's right! All ElectroFlipbrand products purchased through Amazon come with a free no hassle LIFETIME warranty. If there is ever any problem a brand new item is only a few clicks away!
Item_Name: MicroSD Compatible Waterproof HD 1080P Bullet DV Camera for Jet Skiing
Specification: Video, Audio, and Stills: The BulletCam 2.0 packs a ton of features into a compact body. A durable, glass fisheye lens captures a wide field of view, taking both video and still photos at your discretion. Plus, a built-in microphone supplements your stunts with audio, so you'll still hear the cheers of your friends (or fans) every time you play it back., Powerful and Efficient Battery: The BulletCam 2.0's rechargeable lithium-ion battery holds enough power to record continuously for 4 straight hours. We also include a spare battery with the same capacity, so you can get in a whole day of action without needing to recharge. (8 hour potential), Small and Lightweight: The sleek cylindrical body measures only 4x1-inches and weighs only a few ounces, so whether you strap it to your Helmet, Ski Pole, Snowboard, Surfboard, Kayak Paddle, Mountain Bike, or elsewhere, it never gets in the way., Intelligent, Responsive Technology: Focus on the thrill, not on recording it. The BulletCam 2.0 builds in a range of automatic features that work behind the scenes to make sure your video is perfect. This includes automatic white balancing, digital video motion stabilization technology, and three options for exposure control: center-focused, spot-focused, and of course, auto. Plus, all footage includes a watermark so you can quickly recall exactly when your feats took place., Universal Formats for Easy Uploading: Video is recorded in H.264/MPEG-4 format, which is compatible with any operating system and accepted in every common video editing software. Description: The ACCU-ND technology in the Hoya PROND filters yields a truly neutral color balance that will not add any noticeable color-cast to your images. The Hoya PROND series is aimed at the still photography and HDSLR video markets. The series provides 9 filters from two stop to 10 stop light reduction. The Metallic ACCU-ND coating on the PROND filters do not color shift as you move from one density to the next, a common problem with other series of neutral density filters. Now you can set your white balance once and have the same color balance even if you need to change filters due to changes in lighting, or for creative effect. The PROND filters use Hoya's exclusive clear optical glass that has a metallic ACCU-ND coating front and back to create the neutral density affect. Neutral density filters are designed to reduce the amount of light entering your camera lens and should not have any other effect on the image. Reducing the amount of light allows for the use of wider apertures or slower shutter speeds for creative and dramatic effect in bright lighting conditions. All Hoya PROND filters have a low-profile one piece aluminum frame. The thin frame keeps the glass secure and parallel to the sensor while allowing it to be used with super-wide angle lenses.

Specification: Exclusive Hoya ACCU-ND technology ensures accurate color balance when switching between ProND filters, Filter provides "X" amount of neutral density stops (depending on the filter you can insert X-see press release), Manufactured from super high quality "Hoya Clear" optical glass, Assembled using a one-piece aluminum frame creating a rigid, durable, but lightweight filter, Perfect for Still and Video applications,

Description: Take crisp, high quality video in any environment - even underwater - with the portable, durable, thumb-sized HandiCam. The HandiCam is a clever, compact camera that can take on any challenge. Its waterproof case easily endures depths of up to 65 feet, making it perfect for recording your underwater adventures. And of course, it can handle any level of moisture above the surface as well - rain, snow, splashes, and spills are all no match for the HandiCam. To make it ideal for capturing both above-ground or below-the-surface expeditions, the HandiCam builds in hands-free recording and mounts securely to a strong, washable nylon strap that wraps around your head. This gives a great first-person perspective, adding extra flair to your exciting videos. The HandiCam is a small, stylish, and smart solution to the problems posed by oversensitive video cameras and finicky smartphones.    Powerful Battery: The rechargeable lithium-ion battery gets a full boost in no time, and can record for two hours straight if you never hit stop. If you record in smaller bursts, it lasts significantly longer. Comfortable, Washable Strap: The included nylon adjustable strap wraps securely around your head, arm, or leg so you can use the HandiCam hands-free.   That's right! All ElectroFlipbrand products purchased through Amazon come with a free no hassle LIFETIME warranty. If there is ever any problem a brand new item is only a few clicks away!
Item_Name: NEW Digital Video Camera HD Camcorder for Rollerskating + MicroSD Slot
Specification: Built for Adventure: Whether you're on an epic adventure or a relaxing trip, the HandiCam's durable design gives you the power to take home amazing video at the end of the day. Take it on a hike or a climb, out on the waves, under the surface, or anywhere you desire - the built-in wide-angle lens captures a 120-degree field of action, bringing your viewer right into the scene with you., Small and Light: The HandiCam is thumb-sized, measuring only 3x2.5.x2 centimeters. It can get into tight quarters or rest comfortably on your head without weighing you down, whether you're riding a wave or spying on a sunset. Plus, the HandiCam watermarks your footage with the time and date, so you'll be able to show everyone exactly where and when everything happened., High Quality Photos and Video: With an incredible 1280x720 resolution, the HandiCam captures every detail of your adventures. It can take both 30 frames-per-second video and still images, making it the only gadget you'll need to bring along. And if you intend to capture lots and lots of video during your next trip, you can also use high compression mode (848x480 resolution) to allow you to store it all on one card., Super Easy Operation: Operating the HandiCam is simple, straightforward, and fun. The small body has buttons for taking video or stills, power, and compression settings. Indicator lights tell you how much battery you have and whether or not you're recording. And that's all you need. Just mount it, make your selection, and start the action., Universally Compatible: The HandiCam stores your photos and video on MicroSD or MicroSDHC cards inserted into the device. Compatible card sizes range from 2GB - 32GB. These are compatible with pretty much any system, including both Macs and PCs. You can also use the USB attachment to transfer files if you don't want to remove the cards.,
